headline: T. ROWE PRICE INTRODUCES NEW THEMATIC ACTIVE ETF FOCUSED ON COMPANIES LEADING INNOVATION
summary: T. Rowe Price, a global investment management firm and a leader in retirement, announced today the addition of the T. Rowe Price Innovation Leaders ETF (Ticker: TNXT). The new active ETF is designed to provide diversified exposure to companies identified as leaders in innovation across sectors, such as technology, healthcare and financials. It began trading today on the NASDAQ exchange.
